                "imgDesc": "Scylla was prince over the Dragonborn in the distant past. And though he has lost his bodily form, he can still command the currents.<br>When you get within a certain distance of him, you can summon high-speed currents to move to his side. Interact with him and ask him to summon intense currents to send you to a target location.<br>If you aim at specific targets when choosing where to go, he might have other things to say as well...",
